OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781583452
OL,3,CTwo cygnets die after being struck
OL,4,Cduring regatta race
OL,6,FTwo cygnets have died after being
OL,7,Fstruck during a race at the Reading
OL,8,FAmateur Regatta.
OL,10,FThe birds were hit near to Caversham
OL,11,FBridge, where the two day event took
OL,12,Fplace, on Saturday evening (13 June).
OL,14,FLocal charity, Swan Support, said it
OL,15,Fwas 'deeply saddened' by the situation
OL,16,Fand its volunteers are 'working
OL,17,Fconstructively' with those involved to
OL,18,Finvestigate what happened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
