FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781583452
OL,3,CTwo cygnets die after being struck
OL,4,Cduring regatta race
OL,6,FThe incident is currently being
OL,7,Freviewed by the race organisers, along
OL,8,Fwith the King's Swan Marker and other
OL,9,Fauthorities.
OL,11,FSwan Support says it has also notified
OL,12,Fthe Environment Agency and Thames
OL,13,FValley Police.
OL,15,FIn a statement released on Sunday,
OL,16,FSwan Support said: "We are deeply
OL,17,Fsaddened by the loss of the two
OL,18,Fcygnets and concerned by the
OL,19,Fcircumstances of the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781583452
OL,3,CTwo cygnets die after being struck
OL,4,Cduring regatta race
OL,6,F"Our focus now is on working
OL,7,Fconstructively with all relevant
OL,8,Fparties to establish the facts,
OL,9,Fidentify any lessons that can be
OL,10,Flearned, and help reduce the risk of
OL,11,Fsimilar incidents in the future.
OL,13,F"This morning, we met with the race
OL,14,Forganisers to discuss the incident and
OL,15,Fseek clarification on a number of
OL,16,Fimportant matters, including the
OL,17,Fdecision-making process during the
OL,18,Frace and the implementation of the
OL,19,Fagreed wildlife protection measures."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
