PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781583452
OL,3,CTwo cygnets die after being struck
OL,4,Cduring regatta race
OL,6,FThe Reading Amateur Regatta is a
OL,7,Fyearly event and hosts several events
OL,8,Fon the River Thames.
OL,10,FCrews race downstream on a buoyed two-
OL,11,Flane course, ranging from 1500m on
OL,12,FSaturday to 1000m on Sunday.
OL,14,FIt is a volunteer run event, and has
OL,15,Ftaken place in Reading since the mid
OL,16,F1800s.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
