FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1781583452
OL,3,CTwo cygnets die after being struck
OL,4,Cduring regatta race
OL,6,FRaces begin at 9am each morning and
OL,7,Ffinish at 7pm in the evening, with
OL,8,Fmany participants taking part ahead of
OL,9,Fmajor international events later on in
OL,10,Fthe year.
OL,12,FThe event follows the British Rowing
OL,13,FRules of Racing, and also has it's own
OL,14,Fstrict safety rules in place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
